INSTALLATION :

You need xorg headers files
Get the sources
git clone git://github.com/rmdir/xclip-daemon.git
cd xclip-daemon
make and copy xcilpd file wherever you want 
or make install

USAGE :

xcilpd -s /home/joris/clip.sock -n 2000 -d

Then you can use the get command to get
the selections and the del command to clear 
the selection stack.

$ echo "get"|nc -U /path/to/socket.sock
toto
titi
tata
toutou

$ echo "del"|nc -U /home/joris/clip.sock

